{"tid":2134943,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"(26) 電單車交流區 [81]","createTime":"2020-08-01T05:46:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-15T23:22:33.000Z","uid":27487,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"8f5f28c2a0d31e8aa48d87ec53caef2c58841c2b","tid":2134943,"uid":27487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T05:46:15.000Z","msg":"見未有人開，借個靚位 騎劫， 釘橋釘橋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 尋人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n31號係沙駕上堂，20號考個位 <br />\n可唔可以搵搵 <a href=\"http://t.me/bikerrrrr\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fbikerrrrr&d=dD36If%2FKkPZsb%2F00sEqzOUpSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=27921854\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/bikerrrrr</a><br />\n<br />\n*********************************<br />\n<br />\nQ: 想學電單車, 邊間好?<br />\nA: 關於學車問題, 請移玉步至隔離post 「考緊26？你問我答！」<br />\n<br />\nQ: 新牌買咩車好？<br />\nA: 請參考<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VFszC8jutcs&amp;list=PLfxONAWHqrehSVzgiONfbl5GOCQc40V2N&amp;index=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DVFszC8jutcs%26list%3DPLfxONAWHqrehSVzgiONfbl5GOCQc40V2N%26index%3D3&d=dD36If%2FKkPZsb%2F00sEqzOUpSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=f68bf096\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VFszC8jutcs&amp;list=PLfxONAWHqrehSVzgiONfbl5GOCQc40V2N&amp;index=3</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nQ:邊到買車好?<br />\nA: 二手: 28car, facebook marketplace<br />\n新車視乎牌子: (紅色係總代理, 其他係分銷商, 以下為大路牌子)<br />\nHonda: 燦基 (旺角), 恆基 (銅鑼灣), JMCA (土瓜灣)<br />\nYamaha: 萬里達 (太子), 銀星 (深水埗), JMCA (土瓜灣)<br />\nKawasaki: 泰力 (北角), 翔利 (土瓜灣), JMCA (土瓜灣)<br />\nSuzuki: 鈴木科研 (觀塘)<br />\nDucati: Ducati Hong Kong (新蒲崗)<br />\nKTM: KTM Hong Kong (新蒲崗)<br />\nSYM (三陽): 奧士 (大角咀)<br />\nVespa: Motoplex (土瓜灣)<br />\n<br />\n水貨車: DS MOTO (大角咀)<br />\n<br />\nQ: 學車買咩頭盔好？<br />\nA: 睇$做人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大路鋪頭有<br />\n土瓜灣: 車迷 油麻地: 頭盔 元朗/深水埗: 預瘋 九龍城:熊興(Arai代理) 花墟:加利(Shoei代理) <br />\n<br />\nQ: 電單車(26)有咩種類?<br />\nA: 同46一樣, 有分棍波同自動波, 外型大致上可分為:<br />\n<br />\n啡鈴(sport bike)<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 棍波為主, 模仿真實賽車的外型, 坐姿偏高, 騎姿會比較趴, 因為有流線型外殼(fairing)包裹故俗稱啡鈴<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n街車(naked bike)<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 棍波為主(亦有少量自動波款), 坐姿比啡鈴舒適, 適合於市區使用, 因為無外殼所以英文會叫naked bike<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n巡航車(cruiser)<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 棍波為主, 特點係腳踏偏前, 坐姿舒適且坐高低, 適合長時間駕駛<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n綿羊(scooter)<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 自動波為主, 亦細分有龍骨同平地台(無龍骨), 坐姿舒適且靈活, 另外有大容量貯物空間, 適合於市區使用<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n爬雞(dual-sport/off-road)<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 棍波為主, 車身輕而且坐高較高, 主力用於非鋪裝路面(爛路/越野)"},{"pid":"e794577771f86e1939fb65656bbf4f14b93def72","tid":2134943,"uid":80765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T16:22:55.000Z","msg":"有人開左喇 電瓶車交流區<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f4b41cfa0396ed3a812d08373b9fbd6656366b5","tid":2134943,"uid":231957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T15:10:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2836a5114198ce1687ac87cc936cdb3220fb9122","tid":2134943,"uid":11329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T09:06:01.000Z","msg":"有冇人知而家申請學牌要點搞？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57be41a803ab42e4b54e1c315b45035f60baf963","tid":2134943,"uid":206018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2836a5114198ce1687ac87cc936cdb3220fb9122","tid":2134943,"uid":11329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTim